main event: A civilian reported an unidentified flying object in Los Angeles in 1967.
interesting points: No photographs were included in the report, The report contained a handwritten questionnaire asking detailed questions about the sighting, The object was described as being about 30 to 38 feet long with a whitish color, The object emitted a rotating white light at the front and back, The report indicates the object hovered before shooting up and disappearing.
